{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"1":"Purification (Kitab Al-Taharah)"},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":390,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":390}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":196,"arabicnumber":196,"text":"‘Abd Allah ibn ‘Abbas رضي الله عنه a dit que le Prophète ﷺ a bu du lait puis s’est rincé la bouche en disant : « Il y a de la graisse dedans. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (211) Sahih Muslim (358)"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":196}}]}